---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Kovira">
  <div class="relative z-5 flex-1 flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-12 max-w-[640px] mx-auto w-full max-[768px]:px-5 max-[768px]:py-8 overflow-y-auto">
    
    <div class="w-full mb-6 flex justify-start">
      <button onclick="history.back()" class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer bg-transparent border-none p-0">
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5L3 12m0 0l7.5-7.5M3 12h18"></path></svg>
        <span>Back</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-[clamp(24px,_3vw,_36px)] font-extrabold leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.025em] mb-2 text-center text-white">
      <span class="reveal-wrapper">
        <span class="reveal-text delay-1">Privacy Policy</span>
      </span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="text-[11px] text-white/50 text-center mb-10 animate-fade-in delay-2">
      Last updated: June 22, 2026
    </p>

    <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-6 text-left text-white/60 text-xs leading-relaxed animate-fade-in delay-3">
      
      <section class="flex flex-col gap-2 pb-6 border-b border-white/10">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We collect basic registration information (such as your name and email address) when you create an account. For forms created on Kovira, we collect the response submissions on your behalf, acting solely as a data processor.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="flex flex-col gap-2 pb-6 border-b border-white/10">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>
          We use your account information to authenticate you, provide access to the platform, billing, and send updates or support notifications. We do not sell, rent, or trade your data or your submitters' data to any third parties.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="flex flex-col gap-2 pb-6 border-b border-white/10">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">3. Data Retention and Storage</h2>
        <p>
          Your form configuration and response data are stored securely on our encrypted servers. You can permanently delete your responses, forms, or your entire account at any time from your settings panel, which will immediately purge the data from our live systems.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="flex flex-col gap-2 pb-6 border-b border-white/10">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>
          We use essential cookies to maintain your login session. We do not use any third-party advertising trackers or marketing cookies on our application routes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="flex flex-col gap-2 pb-4">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">5. Security Measures</h2>
        <p>
          We implement industry-standard security protocols, including SSL encryption for all data transmission and database level encryption for data at rest. While no system is 100% secure, we regularly audit our architecture to protect your data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="pt-6 border-t border-white/10">
        <p class="text-[11px] text-white/50">
          If you have questions about how we handle user data and personal information, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@kovira.dev" class="text-white hover:underline">privacy@kovira.dev</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
